text: Jordan Corvée (born 13 February 1995) is a French badminton player He began playing badminton in Alençon at aged 6 with his mother and brother Lucas Corvée, and joined France national badminton team in 2016. In 2013, he won silver medal at the European Junior Badminton Championships in mixed team event.
